author: Delenda Joseph
title: Nicki Minaj Confirms Her Relationship Status
text:
Getty Image
No more speculation and rumors . Nicki Minaj and Meek Mill are done, finito, over and done with. The reigning queen of rap confirmed her new relationship status following weeks of scuttlebutt claiming the two had broken up.
“To confirm, yes I am single. Focusing on my work & looking forward to sharing it with you guys really soon. Have a blessed New Year. Love u ”
